{"tid":1572971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"915一役大家都進步了，要贏仲有關鍵的一步","createTime":"2019-09-15T23:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T01:35:17.000Z","uid":50457,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"29b7d9dadef6b39d8f5350ab521af7136174b9e8","tid":1572971,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:20:00.000Z","msg":"和理非，勇武在意識上已經互相包融，不指責，不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n現在，到上場時，記緊齊上齊落，你只要勇敢踏出第一步救手捉，大家最後就會無事<br />\n<br />\n相反，大家如果驚，最後結果亦即是你最唔想的結果，就是團滅同自己都受到不人道對待，自己同樣被捕。<br />\n<br />\n黑警就係知道大家驚，先可以逐一擊破，過往3個月見到30個速龍就可以打散幾千人。<br />\n<br />\n大家不防諗下，有乜可能30個人夠幾千人打，要令自己有勇氣，如果人數遠比速龍多，試下講：<br />\n<br />\n大聲講 <span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;死就死喇，屌你老母，上啊&rdquo;</span> 你要呼喚身邊的手捉，為大家上電<br />\n<br />\n既然唔反抗就必然被捕，點解唔試試踏出勇氣一嗌？<br />\n<br />\n如果人數唔夠，試下講<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;唔夠人啊，下次覆卓，走啊！&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n而唔係講&ldquo;有速龍，快走&rdquo;，&ldquo;我地唔夠打，快走&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n點解打仗咁要求心法, 同士氣，絕不要誇大對方實力令自己方膽怯。<br />\n<br />\n最緊要，試下 <span style=\"color: red;\">大聲啲，嗌出嚟</span><br />\n<br />\n老虎，獅子打交前都會咆哮，細狗見到大狗明知唔夠打都會喪吠，因為雙方對峙，攻心為上。<br />\n<br />\n輸人不輸陣，聲要夠大，除左用嚟壯膽嚇怕對方，亦提升個一刻身邊所有人的勇氣。"},{"pid":"fbaab05f8cdc312cfc3b5ad691a467bb447cf96b","tid":1572971,"uid":313554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:21:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce433145253f26868882ad35c9b7d65314895dea","tid":1572971,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4216e3c8bc5855e69ab3191286a10585701d200e","tid":1572971,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:31:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d575c1f9c8b3770fe26d50090f00caa2831da8c9","tid":1572971,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:35:33.000Z","msg":"講得無錯，佢手扣都唔用啦，人手又唔夠，根本幾千人比佢捉都捉唔到"},{"pid":"2da70bebce8de0a71ee2352f5b886eac27d84f9f","tid":1572971,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:36:50.000Z","msg":"POSH<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a106b623669b6529d4192e205f0e8c87d5153e20","tid":1572971,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d575c1f9c8b3770fe26d50090f00caa2831da8c9","tid":1572971,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:35:33.000Z","msg":"講得無錯，佢手扣都唔用啦，人手又唔夠，根本幾千人比佢捉都捉唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:36:56.000Z","msg":"由說話帶動行為，一定要大聲嗌出嚟"},{"pid":"81a73d80e3da062c051ed5c9076bd27ba25cec59","tid":1572971,"uid":153186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:37:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"892e9b066af387ccc6de519f78fe6d12dd12d5a1","tid":1572971,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a106b623669b6529d4192e205f0e8c87d5153e20","tid":1572971,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d575c1f9c8b3770fe26d50090f00caa2831da8c9","tid":1572971,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:35:33.000Z","msg":"講得無錯，佢手扣都唔用啦，人手又唔夠，根本幾千人比佢捉都捉唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:36:56.000Z","msg":"由說話帶動行為，一定要大聲嗌出嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:40:22.000Z","msg":"做決定往往最難"},{"pid":"dec6335aa354ef90a3b9f020acd15dbf5f919a85","tid":1572971,"uid":30115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:40:56.000Z","msg":"死就死喇，屌你老母，上啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb57ae1fdc744a006b76424b0bfbc0fffed735f","tid":1572971,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:42:33.000Z","msg":"如果你想上就同識嗌 1<br />\n其他人見有人嗌1 可以嗌2<br />\n一路落"},{"pid":"79db6bcdd31f8624ea6c3303cc1570354b476827","tid":1572971,"uid":161025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:44:41.000Z","msg":"死就死 一齊上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要嗌到普及化"},{"pid":"dc41125e7477e01d451af9a967d15babbaadae1e","tid":1572971,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:46:13.000Z","msg":"呢個一定要提，唔好諗住救手足危險就走咗去，分分鐘下次比人捉果個就係你"},{"pid":"ef4df3126e5b2e016d1fe055e4ca484e2c19c0ae","tid":1572971,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54019f42b5613f1211705a9ae81c7ae1e3251558","tid":1572971,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:56:29.000Z","msg":"其實進步左<br />\n依家係起碼咁打返藍絲<br />\n打打下再練大D個膽就會再升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a866fd1877f3575d51bd2bbdfdc768c859499c","tid":1572971,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54019f42b5613f1211705a9ae81c7ae1e3251558","tid":1572971,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:56:29.000Z","msg":"其實進步左<br />\n依家係起碼咁打返藍絲<br />\n打打下再練大D個膽就會再升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:57:21.000Z","msg":"仲有灣仔站燃燒彈"},{"pid":"8d0b1e2b45d024cdb968f805f04e9bc353b9a252","tid":1572971,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:10:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd11dd48024841bfc81d863d2470b00c2428e294","tid